# Map of Bangladesh

This project displays an interactive map of Bangladesh using Leaflet.js. 

## Features
- Highlights the capital, **Dhaka**, with a marker.
- Colors six priority districts: **Chattogram, Feni, Cumilla, Munshiganj, Tangail, and Narshingdi**.
- Interactive popups for all districts.

## How to View
The map should be accessible at: https://chrisczerwonka.github.io/unito_ict4d2026_crashcourse1/ (assuming GitHub Pages is configured to serve from the root of the `main` branch).
